    "title": {
      "rendered": "New Amazon Program Enables Shoppers to Easily Donate to Their Favorite Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-14905\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Amazon Smile\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile.jpg?w=474&amp;ssl=1 474w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><a href=\"https://smile.amazon.com\">AmazonSmile</a> is a new program that enables Amazon shoppers to easily donate 0.5% of their purchases ($.50 per $100 spent) to their favorite U.S.-based nonprofits. With $26.5 billion in sales projected for the fourth quarter for 2013 alone, up to $13.25 million in funds could be raised. Through a partnership with <a href=\"http://www.guidestar.org/\">GuideStar USA</a>, over one million nonprofits are already listed in the AmazonSmile database and all shoppers need to do is search for and then select their favorite nonprofit to have 0.5% of their Amazon purchases donated.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>IMPORTANT Message for Nonprofits:</strong></h2>\n<p>Shoppers can select any 501(c)(3) in the GuideStar USA database, but for the nonprofit to receive the funds, they<a href=\"https://org.amazon.com/ref=_cc_cc\" target=\"_blank\"> must register with AmazonSmile</a>. If you do not register and fund are not claimed within one year, then funds raised will be distributed to other registered nonprofits.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">How to Sign Up for AmazonSmile:</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>1. Visit\u00a0<a href=\"https://smile.amazon.com/\">smile.amazon.com</a>\u00a0and login to your Amazon account.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14912\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Amazon Smile Sign Up\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up.png?resize=600%2C298\" width=\"600\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up.png?resize=300%2C149&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n2.\u00a0Search for and select your favorite nonprofit.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14914\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Amazon Smile Sign Up 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-2.png?resize=600%2C364\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-2.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14915\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Amazon Smile Sign Up 3\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-3.png?resize=600%2C273\" width=\"600\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-3.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-3.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14916\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Amazon Smile Sign Up 4\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-4.png?resize=600%2C216\" width=\"600\" height=\"216\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-4.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-4.png?resize=300%2C108&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>3. If you&#8217;d like to change your selected nonprofit:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14918\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Amazon Smile Sign Up 5\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-5.png?resize=388%2C240\" width=\"388\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-5.png?w=388&amp;ssl=1 388w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Amazon-Smile-Sign-Up-5.png?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 388px) 100vw, 388px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
